The Debian Package burp
----------------------------

BUILD:

 apt-get install debhelper autotools-dev libncurses5-dev libssl-dev \
         zlib1g-dev librsync-dev

 debuild -us -uc

 #check contents

 dpkg-deb -c burp_<version>_<arch>.deb

INSTALL:

 dpkg -i burp_<version>_<arch>.deb

CLEAN (clean git directory):

 ./debian/rules clean
 git clean -n
 # CHECK OUTPUT!!!!
 git clean -f
